Since Xie Wenle's diagnosed
with limited mental capacity,

00:31:21.280 --> 00:31:22.648
regarding sentencing...

00:31:25.120 --> 00:31:27.240
There's nothing more we can do.

00:31:27.520 --> 00:31:29.520
The rest depends
on the prosecutor's office.

