Wu Da framed me.

00:38:08.159 --> 00:38:09.679
And you solved the case

00:38:10.000 --> 00:38:11.599
and brought justice for Xiaole.

00:38:11.920 --> 00:38:13.920
So I feel I should express something.

00:38:13.920 --> 00:38:15.199
Please accept it, okay?

